# Python Chess Game
 Only test in Python 2.7.1 , MacOSX 10.7

## Setup:

See here:  [Python](http://python.org/)

Requirement Package:

[PyGmae](http://www.pygame.org/)
    
[MacOSX install tip][Install PyGmae On MacOSX]

[Install PyGame On MacOSX]:https://bitbucket.org/pygame/pygame/issue/82/homebrew-on-leopard-fails-to-install#comment-627494

## Run:
use this command
>python game.py

to run the game.

## Run Test:
in the root doc. run

>python runtest.py

